headline: Meet 16 Ideal "Safer" September Dividend Dogs Of The S&P500
summary: Sixteen of the thirty-eight highest-yield, 'safer' S&P 500 dividend stocks are highlighted as ready to buy, with adequate free cash flow supporting payouts. Read more here.
